description.narrative: This activity (Global Poverty Action Fund Programme (Phase 1)) is a component of UK Aid Direct Fund - working with small and medium charities reported by FCDO, with a funding type of 'Not for profit organisation' and a budget of £117,967,070. This component benefits Developing countries, unspecified, and works in the following sector(s): Multisector aid. , with the following implementing partners: Coffey International Development, KPMG LLP, MannionDaniels, Triple Line. The start date is 27-10-2010 and the end date is 31-03-2020.
